          "verdict": "findings_remain",
          "findings": [
            {
              "message": "The skill lists the reviewer model as an orchestrator input, but the mandatory “Run exactly” command omits the `--model <reviewer_model>` argument. The wrapper prompt later supplies a reviewer invocation that includes `--model $REVIEWER_MODEL`, so the loaded skill now gives contradictory instructions; an agent following the skill literally can record the round with the profile/default reviewer model instead of the orchestrator-assigned model. Include the model in the canonical command or tell the agent to run the provided reviewer invocation exactly.",
