              "message": "S3/T003 says it will fix \"all call sites in generics_eq.rs\", but the task list only names `fn_sigs_structurally_equal`, `build_combined_canon_map`, and `build_where_form_view`. `build_trait_method_map` also formats function signatures through the same helpers, so omitting it leaves the trait/impl-method comparison path on the pre-fix `impl Trait` behavior and makes the \"all call sites\" claim false.",
